1883.query: SELECT cast(SUM(case when t1.a_gender = 'F' then 1 else 0 end) as real) / SUM(case when t1.a_gender = 'M' then 1 else 0 end), SUM(case when t1.a_quality = 5 then 1 else 0 end), SUM(case when t1.a_quality = 0 then 1 else 0 end) FROM actors as t1 inner JOIN movies2actors as t2 ON t1.actorid = t2.actorid WHERE t2.movieid = 1684910

1884.query: SELECT COUNT(t1.user_id) FROM ratings as t1 inner JOIN movies as t2 ON t1.movie_id = t2.movie_id WHERE t2.movie_title = 'A Way of Life' AND t1.user_trialist = 1

1885.query: SELECT name FROM users WHERE age > 25
